<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Intellectual Property Assignment Agreement</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #2c3e50; }
      .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .section-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.1em;
      }
      .signature-block {
        margin-top: 50px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .signature { width: 45%; }
      .signature-line {
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 5px;
      }
      .signature-underline {
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='header'>
      <h1>INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY ASSIGNMENT AGREEMENT</h1>
      <p>Between {{employerName}} and {{employeeName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>CONTRACT REFERENCE</div>
      <p>Contract ID: {{contractId}}</p>
      <p>Date of Issue: {{issueDate}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>1. PARTIES</div>
      <p><strong>Assignee (Employer):</strong>
        {{employerName}}<br />
        Address: {{employerAddress}}<br />
        Email: {{employerEmail}}</p>
      <p><strong>Assignor (Employee):</strong>
        {{employeeName}}<br />
        Address: {{employeeAddress}}<br />
        Email: {{employeeEmail}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>2. BACKGROUND</div>
      <p>The Employee is engaged as <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> commencing
        <strong>{{startDate}}</strong>. In the course of employment, the Employee
        may create, develop, or contribute to intellectual property. This Agreement
        governs the ownership of such intellectual property.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>3. ASSIGNMENT OF INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</div>
      <p>The Employee hereby irrevocably assigns to the Employer all right, title,
        and interest (including all intellectual property rights) in and to any
        Work Product created during the course of employment. "Work Product" includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Software, code, algorithms, and technical documentation</li>
        <li>Inventions, discoveries, and innovations (whether or not patentable)</li>
        <li>Designs, graphics, and creative works</li>
        <li>Research, reports, data, and analyses</li>
        <li>Business methods, processes, and strategies</li>
        <li>Any other work created using the Employer's resources, time, or information</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>4. SCOPE OF ASSIGNMENT</div>
      <p>This assignment covers Work Product that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Relates to the Employer's current or reasonably anticipated business</li>
        <li>Results from any work performed by the Employee for the Employer</li>
        <li>Is made using the Employer's equipment, facilities, or resources</li>
        <li>Is developed during working hours</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>5. MORAL RIGHTS WAIVER</div>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, the Employee hereby
        waives all moral rights in any Work Product assigned to the Employer,
        including the right to be identified as author and the right to object
        to derogatory treatment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>6. PRIOR INVENTIONS</div>
      <p>The Employee shall disclose to the Employer, prior to commencement of
        employment, any inventions, works, or intellectual property created before
        employment that the Employee wishes to exclude from this Agreement. Any
        undisclosed prior invention that relates to the Employer's business shall
        be deemed included in this assignment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>7. ASSISTANCE AND COOPERATION</div>
      <p>The Employee agrees to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Execute all documents necessary to perfect the Employer's ownership</li>
        <li>Assist with registration of patents, copyrights, or trademarks</li>
        <li>Provide information required to support any intellectual property filing</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These obligations survive termination of employment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>8. CONSIDERATION</div>
      <p>The Employee acknowledges that their salary and employment benefits
        constitute full and adequate consideration for the assignments made
        under this Agreement.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>9. GOVERNING LAW</div>
      <p>This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the Federal Republic
        of Nigeria, including the Copyright Act and Patents and Designs Act.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='signature-block'>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          {{#if employerSignatureImageUrl}}
            <img src='{{employerSignatureImageUrl}}' alt='Employer Signature' style='max-height:60px;max-width:200px;display:block;margin-bottom:6px;' />
          {{else}}
            <div class='signature-underline'></div>
          {{/if}}
          <strong>Employer Signature</strong><br />
          <strong>Name:</strong> {{employerName}}<br />
          {{#if employerSignedAt}}
            <strong>Date:</strong> {{employerSignedAt}}
          {{else}}
            <strong>Date:</strong> _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          {{#if employeeSignatureImageUrl}}
            <img src='{{employeeSignatureImageUrl}}' alt='Employee Signature' style='max-height:60px;max-width:200px;display:block;margin-bottom:6px;' />
          {{else}}
            <div class='signature-underline'></div>
          {{/if}}
          <strong>Employee Signature</strong><br />
          <strong>Name:</strong> {{employeeName}}<br />
          {{#if employeeSignedAt}}
            <strong>Date:</strong> {{employeeSignedAt}}
          {{else}}
            <strong>Date:</strong> _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='footer'>
      <p>Contract processed through JobStack Talent Solutions</p>
      <p>This is a legally binding document. Please read carefully before signing.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
